air:Brand.Name: Economy Flexi
air:Brand.air:Title: Economy Flexi
Flexi
air:Brand.air:Text: Enjoying the ability to change your flight dates for free, the option to cancel and refund your ticket and upgrade your flight with miles to Business Class when you book on Economy Flexi today.

Our Economy Class innovative design minimizes intrusion into your personal space even as the passenger in front reclines; while ergonomic styling of the seat further maximizes knee and legroom. It also features a headrest that can be adjusted as desired for greater support. An easily accessible seatback-mounted handset, personal and non-intrusive reading light and in-seat power supply, are just some of the many intelligent touches designed with you in mind. (Applicable to most aircraft types)
